<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l19">ʒu der <expan>ſelıgenport<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> des <expan>Elwang<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l20">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd laſſen eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l21"><expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Elwang<ex>er</ex></expan> für vns beſant vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒurede geſacʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l22"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> daʒ Jm in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l23">vngütlıch <expan>beſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey vnd beſchehe / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l24">doch ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>r</expan> mit Jm gerett daʒ er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_40_r1l1">dem gerıcht <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_40_r1l2">aufſlag geben </ab><ab facs="#facs_40_r1l3">vnd dıe ſache </ab><ab facs="#facs_40_r1l4">anſteen laſſen wıl </ab></add>
